      |           <ruby>兄<rt>&thinsp;ㄏ丨ㆩ→ㄏ丨ㆩ˫&thinsp;</rt></ruby><ruby>弟<rt>&thinsp;ㄉ丨&thinsp;</rt></ruby>。<ruby>分<rt>&thinsp;ㄏㄨㄣ→ㄏㄨㄣ˫&thinsp;</rt></ruby><ruby>別<rt>&thinsp;ㄅ丨ㄚㆵ&thinsp;</rt></ruby>。<ruby>修<rt>&thinsp;ㄒ丨ㄨ→ㄒ丨ㄨ˫&thinsp;</rt></ruby><ruby>業<rt>&thinsp;ㆣ丨ㄚㆴ̇&thinsp;</rt></ruby>。
